Dime PAC.note: Dime PAC is organized by the Washington State Labor Council.

Justice For All.note: Justice For All is listed for donor purposes under as "Washington State Association for Justice"

Working Families.note: Has spent $337,000 (so far) opposing State Sen. Mark Millet (D-Issaquah).

STRAT PAC.note: The top donors to STRAT PAC are debt collection companies.

US Chamber of Commerce.note: The US Chamber does not disclose donors to its 501(c)6 non-profit, which places it in the category of "dark money."
